## 4. Motion Rules

### Timing: "Snap" Physics

Brutalism does not "ease." Things are either On or Off.

```css
/* Instant transitions */
.transition-instant {
  transition: all 0s;
}

/* OR minimal linear transitions */
.transition-snap {
  transition: all 0.1s linear;
}

/* NO easing functions */
/* ❌ transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; */
/* ❌ transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(...); */
```

### Hover States

```css
/* Background inversion on hover */
.element:hover {
  background: var(--text-primary);
  color: var(--bg-canvas);
  transition: background 0.1s linear, color 0.1s linear;
}
```

### Float Reveal Animation

```css
.index-row-reveal {
  transition: opacity 0.1s linear;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  /* Positioned via JavaScript using mouse coordinates */
}
```

