## 5. Custom Cursor

### Implementation

```css
* {
  cursor: none; /* Hide default cursor */
}

body {
  cursor: none;
}

/* Custom cursor */
.custom-cursor {
  position: fixed;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--text-primary);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  mix-blend-mode: difference;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: transform 0s; /* No easing */
}

/* OR crosshair variant */
.custom-cursor-crosshair {
  position: fixed;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  mix-blend-mode: difference;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.custom-cursor-crosshair::before,
.custom-cursor-crosshair::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  background: var(--text-primary);
}

.custom-cursor-crosshair::before {
  width: 1px;
  height: 100%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.custom-cursor-crosshair::after {
  width: 100%;
  height: 1px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
}
```

### React Component

